snippet.title: TOUHOU SKY ARENA Steam® Version Trailer
snippet.description:
Touhou Project fan game “Touhou Sky Arena” on Steam®!

Enjoy dramatic girl battles in the sky with the "Fired-up Battle System", which changes abilities to the playing song.

Play Network Battles up to 4 players.
Play bombardment battles anytime, anywhere with anyone.
Over 90 tracks recorded with famous Japanese artists like
Rokugen Alice, A-One and BUTAOTOME.

23 characters with each 2 types are available.
Choose your favorite out of all 46 types! 
Rule the sky of Gensokyo with music and bombardments!

Japanese Trailer : https://youtu.be/mdXxRQSdQQ8

◎Steam https://store.steampowered.com/app/1086860/MATSURICLIMAX/
◎Web　http://area-zero.net/product/tsa_climax/en/index.html
